Space shooter v0.0.2 by joined forces
--==----===----===----==--
Controls:
  W - Forward thrust
  S - Reverse thrust
  A - Rotate left
  D - Rotate right
  
  E - Rotate thru weapons
  L - Toggle lights

  SPACE - Shoot lasers !!
  LSHIFT - Afterburners
  
